snippet.title: Gonner 2 - Teaser Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: The IGF winning game GONNER is getting a sequel! GONNER 2 is coming late 2020. Journey your way through deep dark chaotic places with unimaginable sparks of colour as you go on a mission to help Death rid a mysterious presence from her lair. Battle crazy bosses, lose your head (a lot), in this messy, cute, fast-paced procedurally-generated platformer.
